{"tid":745991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶嘈交巧遇前度 男友被打到命危","createTime":"2018-07-17T08:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T11:15:14.000Z","uid":122,"like":317,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"5e780ce19c6ea4d48ed1b6702dd27d128abb90fa","tid":745991,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"【16:00】女事主男友目前情況危殆<br />\n<br />\n一名38歲姓黃女事主，昨晚19:30在九龍城侯王道，因感情問題與同齡及同姓男友爭執，更被男友用手襲擊，女事主受驚逃跑，但數十米外被男友截停，雙方拉扯。剛巧女事主的42歲姓沈前男友途經侯王道，見狀出手阻止，其與該男友互相用手襲擊，途人報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，經初步調查，該前男友涉嫌在公眾地方打架被捕；該男友則涉嫌在公眾地方打架及普通襲擊被捕。案件交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n女事主臉部受傷，與臉部、手及眼部受傷的前男友一同送院治理；該男友同樣臉部受傷昏迷送院。"},{"pid":"a06d78d94745706c206132c14c16ff3b0f22564c","tid":745991,"uid":19933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e5b111aec6d478319d915b91cdd8a5773593b5","tid":745991,"uid":76115,"like":733,"dislike":31,"score":702,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"加埋成三百歲仲搞啲咁嘅野"},{"pid":"694d834f34960320b6e56d3b59d711bc2eba6244","tid":745991,"uid":85751,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7ccac14a1599a3a85bdaa83aaa8f62f6917e5a","tid":745991,"uid":75023,"like":489,"dislike":3,"score":486,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"然後前度又變返現任，現任變前度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffacb00bef73874b8bb4be879c47a922c2c21d3f","tid":745991,"uid":7814,"like":142,"dislike":670,"score":-528,"quote":{"pid":"a1e5b111aec6d478319d915b91cdd8a5773593b5","tid":745991,"uid":76115,"like":733,"dislike":31,"score":702,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"加埋成三百歲仲搞啲咁嘅野"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"38 + 38 + 4